---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Demo — ponens">
  <section class="page-head">
    <h1>Demo</h1>
    <p>Read the reasoning behind a commit. The interactive viewer <strong>zooms</strong> from
      intent-named steps down to atomic actions, with the lineage DAG, the decisions, the policy
      results, and the <strong>residual surface</strong> (the declared gaps). Pick a trace from the
      dropdown — including formally-verified examples with machine-checked proofs and
      counterexamples. Locally, run <code>ponens trace view &lt;file&gt;</code> on any trace.</p>
  </section>
  <div class="viewer-frame">
    <iframe src="/viewer/visualizer.html" title="ponens trace viewer" loading="lazy"></iframe>
  </div>
  <p class="viewer-note">
    Open the example full-screen: <a href="/viewer/visualizer.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">/viewer/visualizer.html ↗</a>
  </p>
</Layout>
